# 18/08/2010 Sebastian Wrede
+ First Internal RSB/IDI C++ prototype with 
  + Support for fully event-driven component communication
  + Extensible Event-Condition-Action abstractions encapsulated in subscriptions
  + Conditions as chains of filters matching event notifications
  + Initial SpreadPort implementation (adapted/extended from ActiveMemory sources)
  + Initial InProcessPort for local communication
  + Initial support for key EDA abstractions (Router, Subscription, AbstractPort, EventProcessor, Filters, ...)
  + Observable Router for optimizations at Port level based on subscription information
  + Integrated serialization of RSBEvents to Google Protocol Buffers and back
  + Extension points for user type conversion and instantiation
  + Config framework taken from XCF sources
  + Basic CMake build config
  + ...

